My CD doesn't have the stars on the front of the CD so i initially thought i got ripped off. But after testing the CD accuraterip confirmed at least 3 other people have ripped a version of my disc. So the only thing i can conclude is that this is an earlier version or a later version. Bummer i really wanted the Stars on the front. This disc is also showing signs of DISC ROT! I had to re-rip this disc 12 times at the slowest speed i could in order to get a 100% error free rip (Thank god for built in error correction). These CD's were made with very low quality CD-Rs and are old, I'm not sure how much longer they will continue to play in the future. My Of June CD-R is destroyed because of disc rot and the chance of getting a clean copy is getting slimmer as the years go on. Owl City - Maybe I'm Dreaming (2008 CD-R Version) After many years i finally own a copy of the original CDBABY release of this beautiful album. My CD doesn't have the stars on the front of the CD so i initially thought i got ripped off. But after testing the CD accuraterip confirmed at least 3 other people have ripped a version of my disc. So the only thing i can conclude is that this is an earlier version or a later version. Bummer i really wanted the Stars on the front. This disc is also showing signs of DISC ROT! I had to re-rip this disc 12 times at the slowest speed i could in order to get a 100% error free rip (Thank god for built in error correction). These CD's were made with very low quality CD-Rs and are old, I'm not sure how much longer they will continue to play in the future. My Of June CD-R is destroyed because of disc rot and the chance of getting a clean copy is getting slimmer as the years go on. The fact i could get a 100% rip of this disc is just pure luck, Track 4 "The Saltwater Room" was the most problematic (Literally kept failing at "04:43") Example of Disc Rot: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xN2LCalHLuE&t=671s&pp=ygUXb3dsIGNpdHkgb2YganVuZSBDRCBSb3Q%3D Anyways the CD has been fully backed up, Artwork scanned/edited in high quality, and is ready for download in the Archive! ENJOY! https://mega.nz/folder/nlUgzYoI#-9sJLh6XeeJ2QJafw8WzoQ
